{
  "stem": "10818.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was the next largest town to which my mother would gravitate from her little town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She couldn't wait to get-- get away from that little town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so she stayed for weeks on end.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they went to this big party given in a B'nai B'rith function.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they met there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a rather interesting courtship, because there was the French occupation in the early '20s.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had to get a-- a permit every time he wanted to come to see her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the same thing, even if she wanted to go away from her little town, she had to get some sort of permit.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In French, yet, which I don't think either of them spoke that well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so they had a meeting place which they talk about, to which, however, they had to have a chaperone to come with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think sometimes they just took a dog.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But it was difficult times, because also the inflation was rampant at the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when they had finally set their wedding date, their-- apparently, their correspondence consisted, you know, buy this kind of soap, because you can now get it, and later on you can't.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And now it's cheaper here, or there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the other thing is in those days, women still had a dowry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my mother's dowry vanished in the inflation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean, it just boom, it just went.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, when my grandmother made an informal will, she stipulated that my mother get an extra portion because she didn't get enough dowry at the time.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were married in 1923.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And actually, my father's stomach ulcer acted up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He contracted it during the war when his two brothers were killed, lots of stress.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
